         Aerostreak looked down on Quasar, who was sent flying backwards 
after her first discharge. "Wow kid, youve got alot to learn!" He helped her 
to her feet and then took out his own plasma pistol and returned fire.

         Hell Beast and Gremlin saw Paralysis, shooting at midair. Quite 
strange, but as they drew closer they saw the exhaust. Scather....
         "Gremlin, you help Paralysis, Im going to help Rampage." He 
commanded, and took off to aid the crab.
